Package chatapp.messages.chat

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Add
    This message is sent to a chatroom by a user who wishes to join that chatroom.
    AddCmd
    This message is sent as a response to the receipt of an IGetCmd message.
    GetCmd
    This message is sent as when a user can not identify the type of the command.
    Quit
    This message is sent to a chatroom by a user who wishes to leave the chatroom.
    StringMsg
    Represents a string (text) message that is sent to a Chatroom.
    UnknownMsg
    Message type for the unknown messages.
    UnknownMsgCmd
    Command for the unknown messages.
